Note:  Also, the the command " }{TEXT 293 6 "coeffs" }{TEXT -1 15 " un
fortunately " }{TEXT 294 8 "does not" }{TEXT -1 36 " pick off the coef
ficients in order." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 4 "The " }{TEXT 260 16 "Binomial Theorem" }{TEXT -1 66 " give
s a formula for finding the coefficients of the expansion of " }
{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(a+b)^n;" "6#),&%\"aG\"\"\"%\"bGF&%\"nG" }{TEXT -1 10 "
  for any " }{TEXT 295 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 53 ".  It is relatively obvious
 that the coefficient of  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "a^k*b^(n-k);" "6#*&)%\"aG%
\"kG\"\"\")%\"bG,&%\"nGF'F&!\"\"F'" }{TEXT -1 19 "  for any value of \+
" }{TEXT 296 1 "k" }{TEXT -1 11 " from 0 to " }{TEXT 297 1 "n" }{TEXT 
-1 46 " is given by the number of ways we can choose " }{TEXT 298 1 "k
" }{TEXT -1 8 " of the " }{TEXT 300 1 "a" }{TEXT -1 12 "'s from the " 
}{TEXT 299 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 1 " " }{TEXT 301 1 "a" }{TEXT -1 20 "'s in \+
the expansion " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(a+b)*(a+b)" "6#*&,&%\"aG\"\"\"%\"bGF&
F&,&F%F&F'F&F&" }{TEXT -1 7 " ....( " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(a+b)" "6#,&%\"a
G\"\"\"%\"bGF%" }{TEXT -1 4 " ), " }{TEXT 302 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 41 " tim
es .   The number of combinations of " }{TEXT 303 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 18 "
 objects choosing " }{TEXT 304 1 "k" }{TEXT -1 12 " at a time, " }
{XPPEDIT 18 0 "nCk" "6#%$nCkG" }{TEXT -1 27 ", is given by the formula
  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "nCk=n!/(k!*(n-k)!)" "6#/%$nCkG*&-%*factorialG6#%\"
nG\"\"\"*&-F'6#%\"kGF*-F'6#,&F)F*F.!\"\"F*F2" }{TEXT -1 2 " ." }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 262 10 "State th
e " }{TEXT 261 16 "Binomial Theorem" }{TEXT -1 1 " " }{TEXT 305 31 "an
d use Maple to demonstrate it" }{TEXT -1 1 "." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 8 "Compute " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "
sum(binomial(n,k),k=0..n)" "6#-%$sumG6$-%)binomialG6$%\"nG%\"kG/F*;\"
\"!F)" }{TEXT -1 34 "  for n=1 to 10.  Here the symbol " }{XPPEDIT 18 
0 "Sigma;" "6#%&SigmaG" }{TEXT -1 70 " (Greek letter Sigma) stands for
 sum.   (See the worksheet SumSeq.mws)" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "
